text: Charata Airport is an airport serving the town of Charata in the Chaco Province of Argentina. The airport is at the western edge of Charata. The airport has crossing runways. Runway 10/28 is only partially marked. ==See also== * * *Transport in Argentina *List of airports in Argentina ==References== ==External links== *OpenStreetMap - Charata *OurAirports - Charata Airport * Category:Airports in Chaco Province
